description	"Darth Vader

^2Weaponry:
- Darth Vader's Lightsaber [EP4]
-- ^1Red ^7/ ^6Purple ^7Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense (2)
-- Blaster Deflect (3)
-- Saber Throw (3) ^3[CS1]

^5Force Powers:
