- Sense (3)
- Grip  (3)

^8Attributes:
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (2)

Darth Vader has taken command of all the available units to attack the Rebel base of Yavin.  He is seeing to it personally that all captured Rebels suffer for destroying the Death Star during the Battle of Yavin, with eyes set especially on Luke Skywalker."